Uses of Package
de.fu.weave

Packages that use de.fu.weave
de.fu.scetris.data   
de.fu.scetris.data.formsupport   
de.fu.scetris.web Contains all stuff directly involved with the web-application (the business logic). 
de.fu.scetris.web.forms   
de.fu.scetris.web.showcase A sample-package demonstrating the use of auto generated forms. 
de.fu.weave Weave is a tiny web-framework for Java which is developed along with Scetris myCourses during the SCORE Contest 2011. 
de.fu.weave.impl Implementations. 
de.fu.weave.impl.frigg The main implementation of weave (targets Java Servlets and XSL-T as Template Engine) 
de.fu.weave.orm Provides classes for Object-Relational-Mapping. 
de.fu.weave.output Output-Converters are used to convert the output of a weave controller into a format suitable for presentation. 
de.fu.weave.reflect Provides Classes for reflecting modules of a web-application 
de.fu.weave.tests
